iple new intents; the guardian asks whether the new set together preserves the kernel. Each operation type gets a per-operation prompt with worked accept/reject examples (over-train first, then scale back), and must always return well-formed NOTA via a generated verdict grammar, closed rejection set, parse-and-retry, and shape test. A specialized clean-context trained guardian outperforms the noise-buried submitting agent even on a weaker model; specialization beats raw model strength.|] High High Zero [guardian admission-control supersede nota spirit intent-capture])) (4oev ([(Technology (Software (Distributed ProtocolDesign)))] Principle [There should be no NOTA between components. Daemons and components exchange binary protocol data; the CLI is the translation/debugging surface that can wrap a normal call in a debugging request with options such as where logs should be displayed or stored. *IPC*] High High Zero [nota ipc cli daemon])) (3chp ([(Technology (Software (Distributed ProtocolDesign)))] Decision [The policy and control socket in triad components should be called the meta socket, not the owner socket. *IPC*] High Medium Zero [meta-socket ipc triad])) (bwxn ([(Technology (Software (Distributed ProtocolDesign)))] Constraint [Spirit should not call the referent guardian when a referent registration request names an already registered referent; existing registry state settles that request without LLM judgment. *admission control*] High Medium Zero [spirit referent-guardian admission-control])) (xf25 ([(Technology (Software (Distributed ProtocolDesign)))] Correction [Spirit without a configured guardian fails closed rather than accepting ungated writes. *admission control*] Medium Medium Zero [spirit guardian admission-control])) (7l7l ([(Technology (Software (Distributed ProtocolDesign)))] Decision [|Sema classification vocabulary stays internal to sema-engine execution and observation, off the public contract wire. Contract operation roots are domain verbs a